{"lemma":"أَشِرَّةٍ","slug":"أَشِرَّةٍ","root":"ش.ر.ر","root_slug":"ش-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21998","n831"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"evil"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"very evil; villainous"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"(with ال (al-, “the”)) the Evil One, Satan, the Devil"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a mischievous person, a villain","tags":["countable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21998","headword_ar":"اشرّهُ","root":"$r","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attributed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imputed, to him evil, wrongdoing, injustice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) but some disallow this. (S. [See also 1.]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ar~uwhu","text_ar":"اَشَرُّوهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They banished him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drove him away, and caused him to be alone."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also 1, latter part, in two places. ―         -b2-  [Hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$r~hu","text_ar":"اشرّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He manifested it, revealed it, published it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it known."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) Thus in a verse of Imra-el-Keys, where he says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo yu$ir~uwna maqotaliY","text_ar":"لَوْ يُشِرُّونَ مَقْتَلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that they might publish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make known, my slaughter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as related by As; but it is better with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"s","text_ar":"س"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^a$ar~ahu","text_ar":"مَا اَشَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA $ar~ahu","text_ar":"مَا شَرَّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [the latter of which is extr. with respect to form, but more commonly used than the former, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How evil, wrongdoing, unjust, bad, corrupt, wicked, mischievous, vitious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depraved, is he!"},{"kind":"text","text":"] phrases similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^axoyarahu","text_ar":"مَا اَخْيَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA xayorahu","text_ar":"مَا خَيْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which have the contr. meaning]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xyr","text_ar":"خير"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n831","headword_ar":"اُشْرَةٌ","root":"A$r","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and its dual: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=$irN","text_ar":"ا=شِرٌ"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}